        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart" subtype="chapter">
                    <ab><title>Genesis 49</title>
                        <milestone unit="line" xml:id="Gen049-P50v-L23" n="23"
                            prev="JSul.IV.02A.001.048.xml#Gen048-P50v-L23" />
                        <l n="1" xml:id="Gen-049-001"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויקרא </foreign>
                            Da čaqyrdy Jaʿaqov oɣlanlaryn da ajtty toplanyŋyz da aŋlatajym
                            <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                            sizgä neni ki učrar sizgä aḫyrynda ol günlärniŋ.</l>
                        <l n="2" xml:id="Gen-049-002"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">הקבצו </foreign>
                            Da toplanyŋyz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            da ešitiŋiz ej oɣlanlary Jaʿaqovnyŋ da ešitiŋiz<ref n="1"
                                target="#Gen-049-fn1" type="noteAnchor" /> sözinä Jisraʾel
                            ataŋyznyŋ.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                        <l n="3" xml:id="Gen-049-003"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ראובן </foreign>
                            Ej Ruʾuven tuŋɣučym ediŋ sen quvatym da ilki güčimniŋ saŋa
                            <milestone unit="page" n="51r" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            jaqyšyrdy zejada syj da zejada ḥörmät.</l>
                        <l n="4" xml:id="Gen-049-004"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">פחז </foreign>
                            Tek aqqan suv gibi ašyqtyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            ḥörmätli olmadyn ki čyqtyn jataɣyna ataŋnyŋ ol vaqyt ki jeŋil idtiŋ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            jataɣymny jataɣym hörmätiŋni kesti.</l>
                        <l n="5" xml:id="Gen-049-005"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">שׁמעון </foreign>
                            Šimʿon da Levi arqardaš oldular
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            zülüm silaḥlarylan ḥalqyna dirlik jerläriniŋ.</l>
                        <l n="6" xml:id="Gen-049-006"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בסודם </foreign>
                            Ǯemlärinä girmädi ǯanym
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            da ǯyjynlaryna birikmädi ḥörmätli ǯanym tek gendi ačuvlary ilän
                            öldürdilär Šeḫem
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            ḥalqyny da kiläkläri ilän kestilär temälni<ref n="2"
                                target="#Gen-049-fn2" type="noteAnchor" />.</l>
                        <l n="7" xml:id="Gen-049-007"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ארור </foreign>
                            Eḫsik olsyn deji ačuvlary
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            ki keskindir da qaḥerläri ki qatydyr böläjim alarny Jaʿaqovda da daɣytajym
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            alarny Jisraʾeldä.</l>
                        <l n="8" xml:id="Gen-049-008"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">יהורה </foreign>
                            Ej Juhuda sen maḫtovly maḫtarlar seni qardašlaryŋ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            qoluŋ ola eŋsäsindä dušmanlaryŋnyŋ baš uralar saŋa oɣlanlary
                            ataŋnyŋ.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                        <l n="9" xml:id="Gen-049-009"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">גור </foreign>
                            Aslan javrysy gibisin Juhuda butardan qutulup oɣlum selamät čyqtyŋ čöḫär
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            da jatyr selamet aslan gibi da jigit aslan gibi da kim turɣuza bilir
                            any.</l>
                        <l n="10" xml:id="Gen-049-010"><supplied reason="lost"><foreign
                                    xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">לא</foreign>
                            </supplied> Getmäz
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ḥöḫümdärlik Juhudadan da resim jazyǯysy ḥökümdärligi arasyndan deginǯä ki
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            gelir ḥarablyɣy Šilonyŋ da aŋar olyr itaḥatlyɣy uluslarnyŋ.</l>
                        <l n="11" xml:id="Gen-049-011"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">אסרי </foreign>
                            Baɣlar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            baɣ kütükgä išägin da syjly baɣ butaɣyna diši ešäk javrusyn juvar šarap
                            <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                            ilän urbasyn da qyrmyzy jüzüm suju ilän perdäsin.</l>
                        <l n="12" xml:id="Gen-049-012"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">חכלילי </foreign>
                            Qyrmyzylyɣy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            gözlärniŋ (čeḥräniŋ) šarapdan da aqlyɣy dišlärniŋ süttän.</l>
                        <l n="13" xml:id="Gen-049-013"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">זבולון </foreign>
                            Zevulun jaqyt
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            limanyna deŋizlärniŋ qonar da ol synordaš duraq limanyna gemilärniŋ da kenary
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            synorunyŋ Čidonɣa degin.</l>
                        <l n="14" xml:id="Gen-049-014"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ישׂשׂכר </foreign>
                            Jišsaḫar qalyn süj<supplied reason="lost">ä</supplied>kli<ref n="3"
                                target="#Gen-049-fn3" type="noteAnchor" /> raḥat jatyr ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                            ordular arasyna.</l>
                        <l n="15" xml:id="Gen-049-015"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וירא </foreign>
                            Da gördi raḥatlyqny ki ejidir da ol jer išlämäkni
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            ki tatlydyr da qajyrdy omuzuny jük kötärmä da oldu ḥaraǯny veriǯi da qullyq
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            etiǯi.</l>
                        <l n="16" xml:id="Gen-049-016"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">דן ידין </foreign>
                            Dan šaraʿat idär ulusuna birsi gibi ševetläriniŋ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            Jisraʾelniŋ.</l>
                        <l n="17" xml:id="Gen-049-017"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">יהי דן </foreign>
                            Olyr Dan jylan gibi jol üstünä oq jylany gibi soq<supplied reason="lost"
                                >m</supplied>aq<ref n="4" target="#Gen-049-fn4" type="noteAnchor" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            üstünä ol tikken oqčalaryn atnyŋ da jyqylyr atlanuvčysy artqary.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                        <l n="18" xml:id="Gen-049-018"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">לישׁועתּךָ </foreign>
                            Qutarmaɣyna išandym ej YWY.</l>
                        <l n="19" xml:id="Gen-049-019"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">גד </foreign>
                            Gad ǯyjyn ǯyjylyrsa aŋar da
                            <milestone unit="line" n="25" />
                            ol ǯyjylyp kesär ol ǯyjynny soŋra.</l>
                        <l n="20" xml:id="Gen-049-020"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">מאשׁר </foreign>
                            Ašer semiz topraɣyndan ašar ašyny
                            <milestone unit="line" n="26" />
                            da ol verir sefaʿaly ašlaryn ḫannyŋ.</l>
                        <l n="21" xml:id="Gen-049-021"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">נפתּלי </foreign>
                            Serbaz sügün gibi ol
                            <milestone unit="page" n="51v" />
                            <milestone unit="line" n="1" />
                            veriǯi olur tatly ḥabar ajtuvlar.</l>
                        <l n="22" xml:id="Gen-049-022"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בּן פּרתּ </foreign>
                            Jajylaj turɣan baɣ kütükniŋ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="2" />
                            butaɣy gibi Josef jajylaj turɣan baɣ kütükniŋ butaɣy gibi češmä janynda
                            <milestone unit="line" n="3" />
                            anǯa butaqlary her birsi atlap čyqty qala üstünä.</l>
                        <l n="23" xml:id="Gen-049-023"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">וימררוהו </foreign>
                            Da aǯy
                            <milestone unit="line" n="4" />
                            idti idilär aŋar da oq ataǯaq oldular da dušman olup sattylar any oq
                            <milestone unit="line" n="5" />
                            jaj saḥablary.</l>
                        <l n="24" xml:id="Gen-049-024"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ותּשׁב </foreign>
                            Da oturdu güčli Nilgä jaqyn jaʿasy bilän da quvatlandylar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="6" />
                            biläkläri qollarynyŋ qudratyndan güčli Täŋrisiniŋ Jaʿaqovnyŋ andan čyqty čoban
                            <milestone unit="line" n="7" />
                            temäl da iš Jisraʿelniŋ.</l>
                        <l n="25" xml:id="Gen-049-025">(<foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">משׁה</foreign>
                            ) <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">מאל </foreign>
                            Täŋrisindän ataŋnyŋ oldu ki jardym idti
                            <milestone unit="line" n="8" />
                            saŋa da qadir Täŋridän olɣaj da alɣyšlaɣaj seni beräkätläri ilän
                            göklärniŋ joqarydan
                            <milestone unit="line" n="9" />
                            beräkätlärin derjanyŋ ki jatajdyr diptä beräkätlärin emčäklärniŋ da
                            qursaqnyŋ.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="10" />
                        <l n="26" xml:id="Gen-049-026"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ברכות אביךָ </foreign>
                            Alɣyšlary ataŋnyŋ mamyr oldular alɣyšlaryndan atalarymnyŋ nišanyna
                            <milestone unit="line" n="11" />
                            degin qajalarynyŋ dunjanyŋ olɣajlar bašyna Josefniŋ da töpäsinä ɣunaḥtan
                            <milestone unit="line" n="12" />
                            ajrylɣanynyŋ qardašlarynyŋ.</l>
                        <l n="27" xml:id="Gen-049-027"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בנימן </foreign>
                            Binjamin börü gibi butarlar
                            <milestone unit="line" n="13" />
                            ertä bilän ašar olǯa da ʿaḫšamda paj idär savɣa.
                            <milestone unit="line" n="14" />
                            (<foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בבקר שׁאול
                                במלכותּ</foreign>
                            ) (<foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">בערב מרדכי
                                בגלות</foreign>
                            )</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="15" />
                        <l n="28" xml:id="Gen-049-028"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">כל אלה </foreign>
                            Ǯümlä bular ševetläri Jisraʾelniŋ on eki da budyr ne ki sözlädi
                            <milestone unit="line" n="16" />
                            alarɣa atalary da alɣyšlady alarny här kišini ilajyq alɣyšyna görä alɣyšlady
                            <milestone unit="line" n="17" />
                            alarny.</l>
                        <l n="29" xml:id="Gen-049-029"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויצו </foreign>
                            Da vasyta idti alarɣa da ajtty alarɣa men ǯem olunaǯaɣym ulusyma
                            <milestone unit="line" n="18" />
                            gömüŋiz meni atalarym janyna ol maʿarada ki düzündä ʿEfronnyŋ ol
                            Ḥitili.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="19" />
                        <l n="30" xml:id="Gen-049-030"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">במערה </foreign>
                            Maʿarada ki düzündä ol Maḫpelanyŋ ki aldyna Mamreniŋ
                            <milestone unit="line" n="20" />
                            jerindä Kenaʿannyŋ ki satyn aldy Avraham ol tarlovny janyndan ʿEfronnyŋ ol
                            <milestone unit="line" n="21" />
                            Ḥitili tutuvluɣyna zerätniŋ.</l>
                        <l n="31" xml:id="Gen-049-031"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">שׁמה </foreign>
                            Anda gömdilär Avrahamny da Sara ḫatynyn
                            <milestone unit="line" n="22" />
                            anda gömdilär Jičḥaqny da Rivqa ḫatynyn da anda gömdim Leʾany.</l>
                        <l n="32" xml:id="Gen-049-032"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">מקנה</foreign>
                            <milestone unit="line" n="23" />
                            Mülkligini ol tarlovnyŋ da ol maʿara ki andan janyndan oɣlanlarynyŋ
                            Ḥetniŋ.</l>
                        <milestone unit="line" n="24" />
                        <l n="33" xml:id="Gen-049-033"><foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">ויכל </foreign>
                            Da bittirdi Jaʿaqov väsäjät etmä oɣlanlaryna da toplady ajaqlaryn ol
                            <milestone unit="line" xml:id="Gen049-P51v-L25" n="25"
                                next="JSul.IV.02A.001.050.xml#Gen050-P51v-L25" />
                            töš<supplied reason="lost">ä</supplied>kkä<ref n="5"
                                target="#Gen-049-fn5" type="noteAnchor" /> da ǯany čyqty da ǯem
                            olundy uluslaryna.</l>
                    </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="apparatus">
                <listApp>
                    <app>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-049-fn1" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A: Spelled <foreign
                                xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">אשִׁיטִיגִיז</foreign>
                            ; a scribal error.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-049-fn2" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A: A mistranslation. In
                            Gen 49:6 the Biblical Hebrew <foreign xml:lang="he"
                                style="unicode-bidi: embed;">שׁוֹר </foreign>
                            stands for ‘bullock, steer’ (Koehler &amp; Baumgartner 1985: 958).
                            However, there exists a common mistranslation among some Karaim Bible
                            translations since they render a slightly different Biblical Hebrew word
                                <foreign xml:lang="he" style="unicode-bidi: embed;">שׁוּר </foreign>
                            ‘wall’ (Koehler &amp; Baumgartner 1985: 958). | BSMS 288:
                                <emph>qalany</emph>. | ADub.III.73: <emph>kermenni</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-049-fn3" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A: <emph>süjkli</emph>;
                            a scribal error. | BSMS 288: <emph>süjäkli</emph>. | ADub.III.73:
                                <emph>süvekli</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-049-fn4" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A: <emph>soqaq</emph>;
                            probably a scribal error. | BSMS 288: <emph>soqmaq</emph>.</note>
                        <note xml:id="Gen-049-fn5" type="footnote">JSul.IV.02A: <emph>töškkä</emph>;
